  <h2 id="verdict" class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Quick Verdict</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Both platforms connect you with real tutors for 1-on-1 lessons, but they serve different types of learners. iTalki has more tutors, lower prices, and a wider variety of teaching styles. Preply offers more structure, better native-speaker options, and a more polished learning experience. For most learners on a budget, iTalki is the better choice. For learners who want formal curriculum and guaranteed quality, Preply has the edge.</p>

